{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"headers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"url","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed."}]}],"name":"headers"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This is useful for:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Regional compliance"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Network monitoring","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Firewall restrictions"}]},{"type":"text","text":": Work around corporate firewall rules"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"while preserving all headers and request body content.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active."}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:headers:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PWConfiguration"}}}